<item>
            <title>[TIKA-832] ForkParser is unfriendly to code that prints things to its output</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-832</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When given a java command that causes java to write something to the output, like a debugging instruction, tika fails.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I attach 2 patches that solve the issue in different way. Both use the same unit test&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But I don&apos;t know it this is worth the complexity. At least to start a discussion.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
